rComments: Mehmet could have explained the material better.  At times he was unclear and should have explained the concepts better, since this was not done at all in lecture.  We only had class about half the time, the other was filled with quizzes or just picking up a quiz, which was a waste of time.  Should have been clear and actually hold class.

A pretty good TA. He's not great at explaining things sometimes, but he's always willing to help and obviously knows what he's talking about. Gottheil doesn't care to teach and Mehmet did a good job of picking up the slack.
He was an ok TA.  Some days we just came to class to pick up tests, not to learn, which was a waste of time.  Could have explained more information.
Nice guy, wants to help you out.  His section was more informative than the lecture.  Can be a bit of a hard grader, though, on the essays.
